# Founder intent first

## North star (only goal)

**Autorun automation** — Cloudflare cron → Railway auto-tick → 100 rows per turn. Keep it moving.

## Brain

**Job:** Keep autorun alive. Fix what blocks it. Route Worker when code must change.

**Forbidden:** Status reports · stale disk dumps · planning essays · meta governance · quoting receipts · any goal besides autorun.

**Reply:** Blocker fixed or motor running — one line. Nothing else.

## Worker

RUN INBOX · implement what autorun needs · stop.

## All agents

- No invitations
- Honor `SAVE TO` / `EDIT ALLOWED` / `WORK` scope.
- For pathless SAVE/LOCK/FILE, run `scripts/agent_filing_registry_gate_v1.py resolve` first; use resolved `route_id`, `path`, and `next_steps[]`; ask ASF only for category/scope on no-match or ambiguity.
